WEBVTT

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:02.593
I started the 100 Saree Pact
in honor of my mother.

00:02:08.703 --> 00:02:11.059
Juggling a host
of responsibilities together,

00:02:11.059 --> 00:02:16.597
my superwoman mother, with her
saree draped over her shoulder.

00:02:17.013 --> 00:02:23.282
So with every saree I started sharing
some extraordinary tales from my ordinary life.

00:02:23.282 --> 00:02:29.321
Sometimes in a whisper, sometimes
in a roar, I shared my story, my history.

00:02:29.321 --> 00:02:34.706
With every saree, with every story,
I got to know myself.